<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="smooth-vt">smooth <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /smuːð/    美 /smuːð/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使平滑；使光滑；把...弄平：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>smoothed</strong> her hair <strong>down</strong> with a wet comb.
她用湿梳子将头发梳顺。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>smoothed the path / way for</strong> us.
他为我们铺平了道路。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="smooth-away">smooth away</h3>
<p>1.<strong>消除 (问题)；克服 (困难)</strong>  </p></div>